display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> as follows:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[  \begin {aligned}     \mathopen {}\left \lvert g^*\mathcal {A}\right \rvert \mathclose {}  &:\equiv  B\\   x \approx _{g^*\mathcal {A}} y &:\equiv  gx \approx _{\mathcal {A}} gy\\   \mathsf {rx}_{g^*\mathcal {A}}x &:\equiv  \mathsf {rx}_{\mathcal {A}}  \mathopen {}\left \lparen gx\right \rparen \mathclose {}   \end {aligned} ]]></fr:tex>
 
   
