display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\textstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\scriptstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:B\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}gx\approx _{\mathcal {A}}gy]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link
