href="erct-001I.xml"
addr="erct-001I"
title="Proposition">proposition</fr:link>. But this is a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-001I.xml"
addr="erct-001I"
title="Proposition">retract</fr:link> of  <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\textstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\scriptstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{  \mathopen {}\left \lparen y:A\right \rparen \mathclose {} }}gx\approx _{\mathcal {A}}y]]></fr:tex>, which is a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-001I.xml"
addr="erct-001I"
title="Proposition">proposition</fr:link> by the univalence of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex>; thus the result follows from the closure of <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-001I.xml"
addr="erct-001I"
title="Proposition">propositions</fr:link> under <fr:link
